OL,3,CNew council leader says Birmingham bin
OL,4,Cstrike firings would be 'sign of
OL,5,Cfailure'
OL,7,FThe new leader of Birmingham City
OL,8,FCouncil has said dismissing striking
OL,9,Fbin workers would be a "sign of
OL,10,Ffailure" - but has stopped short of
OL,11,Fruling the option out entirely.
OL,13,FAs he pledged to find a resolution to
OL,14,Fthe long-running dispute, Roger Harmer
OL,15,Fsaid securing a deal was his "number
OL,16,Fone priority".
OL,26,@qD@XOUrD@HO]wD@^OUxD@MO]
