OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1781028676
OL,3,CNew council leader says Birmingham bin
OL,4,Cstrike firings would be 'sign of
OL,5,Cfailure'
OL,7,FCllr Harmer, who took control of the
OL,8,Fcouncil on Friday (5 June) as head of
OL,9,Fa coalition involving the Liberal
OL,10,FDemocrats, Greens and independents,
OL,11,Fsaid ending the strike was a key focus
OL,12,Ffor the new administration.
OL,14,FThe industrial action, which has
OL,15,Fdisrupted waste collections across
OL,16,FBirmingham for more than a year, has
OL,17,Fbecome one of the biggest challenges
OL,18,Ffacing the city.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/8
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,376,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F375A1781028676
OL,3,CNew council leader says Birmingham bin
OL,4,Cstrike firings would be 'sign of
OL,5,Cfailure'
OL,7,FSpeaking on his first full day in the
OL,8,Frole, Cllr Harmer said he wanted to
OL,9,Fsecure "a resolution that's fair".
OL,11,F"That is absolutely not what we're
OL,12,Faiming to do," he said, when asked
OL,13,Fabout the possibility of dismissing
OL,14,Fworkers.
OL,16,F"That would be a sign of failure if we
OL,17,Fgot to that point."
OL,19,FHowever, he stopped short of ruling
OL,20,Fout sackings completely.
OL,26,@qD@HOUqD@aO]sD@AOUtD@NO]xD@AOUyD@SO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/8
