OL,3,CNew council leader says Birmingham bin
OL,4,Cstrike firings would be 'sign of
OL,5,Cfailure'
OL,7,FThe administration will still need
OL,8,Fsupport from other parties to pass
OL,9,Fmeasures through the council chamber.
